        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI see you're picking up the latest images change in drools and engine I made, hopefully will work.\n\nQuestion, upgrading to the docker version, does it solve the problem then with manually needing to pull the policy-common image manually as I had in in the other csit parallel review.   At least that's what it looks like.  Can you confirm?   Or what problems does it solve to upgrade the docker version for my own understanding?",
